HEADWORD: Roommate
<hw>Room"mate`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One of two or more
occupying the same room or rooms; one who shares the occupancy of a room
or rooms; a chum.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

